Package tree

Class Tree<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tree.Tree<T>
  • public class Tree<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a tree data structure that stores generic values T. Provides methods for adding/removing nodes, traversing the tree, etc.
